=== Implementation Notes ===

- Modified SpillReplay to accept publisher (*Publisher) alongside CHWriter.
- replayFile now reconstructs Tick/Bar from spillEntry, sets IsReplay=true,
  and calls publisher.PublishTick/PublishBar before chWriter.EnqueueTick/Bar.
- ADR-0009 §2.1: publisher first (so NATS subscribers see data before CH write
  completes), matching the order in Manager.HandleTick.
- SpillEntry format is sparse (UserID/AccountID/SymbolRaw not stored in spill
  JSONL). Reconstructed DTOs use empty strings for these fields — acceptable
  for replay (CH columns are LowCardinality(String) accepting empty).
- X-Ant-Replay:1 header is set automatically by publisher when IsReplay=true
  (from M10.2-1).

Files changed:
- backend/internal/mdgateway/spill_replay.go (publisher injection + dual-write logic)
